Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.94,0:00:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生…日？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.71,0:00:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一大意就忘了問妳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才發現
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是還沒過就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼時候呢？妮依娜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.15,0:00:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.42,0:00:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就定在9月7日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那天放假，來辦個生日會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳想想看想要什麼禮物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.88,0:00:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝爾蓋，你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.38,0:00:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.52,0:00:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝爾蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.56,0:01:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以背叛我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.10,0:01:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.40,0:01:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之你去處理那件工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.07,0:01:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託找出真正的公主喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.91,0:01:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.04,0:01:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠控制那個的人\N就可以稱霸世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要加稅啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在女王強迫之下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.06,0:01:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,議會只能通過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.76,0:01:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像因為即位典禮和整修城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.03,0:01:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓國庫相當吃緊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.63,0:01:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了慶祝女王生日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.80,0:01:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要全國上下舉辦活動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.37,0:01:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個活動的資金大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.57,0:01:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失業率已經攀升了\N還真是悠哉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃，記得女王的生日是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得記住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.42,0:02:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的公主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.34,0:02:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到夢想了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心悸動無法平息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶物誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿盈內心 開始散放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.36,0:02:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何會如此不安呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法控制的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人不禁落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:03:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朝一日一定會抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算中途受挫也不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣向前邁進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能踏出小小的一步 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.04,0:03:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嶄新的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第11話 生日☆快樂\N真的嚇了一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡竟然一口氣衝到20幾名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.89,0:03:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是依琳娜和埃爾斯的功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要一邊吃東西一邊講話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這種人會是29名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.97,0:03:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她獨自挑戰健行考試
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還最快走完全程嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.05,0:04:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯，打起精神啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.99,0:04:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不能重考
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30名還是很棒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫妳任何事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後大家一起抓住夢想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳，愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後妮娜和巴\N則是維持1，2名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是以平常心應試而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.41,0:04:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也真想說一次這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在最頂點\N說著“我只是平常心”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏匿科學技術
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭曲世界的元兇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話真是刺耳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然已經將植入體內型的\N奈米機械控制方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分析到那種程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還沒有舞鬥服和物質化的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不知道能撐到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們為什麼就是不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一心一意追求力量的話\N只會走上毀滅一途啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份資料的內容也讓人很擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑谷到底是\N受到誰委託而行動的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.50,0:05:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是卡迪亞就是佛羅倫斯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從那個管風琴響過之後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.44,0:05:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都疑神疑鬼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平這種東西真是脆弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.18,0:05:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了得到和平
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就不知道\N犧牲多少乙HiME了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會陪著夏樹的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.29,0:05:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.00,0:06:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個，妳明天生日對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.77,0:06:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不嫌棄的話\N請收下禮物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.11,0:06:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜生日啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.84,0:06:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.84,0:06:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜跟真白女王\N同一天生日了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白也生日啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來\N當然要辦一場宴會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宴會～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.99,0:06:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不用了啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.56,0:06:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，妳只要\N笑著說很高興就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜真是一點也不坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.07,0:06:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算考完試了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也瘋過頭了點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·王，愛莉卡·夢宮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事情要跟妳們說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:07:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被指派工作了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.16,0:07:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天有某個國家的王子要來學園
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是日邦格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大陸最東方的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.67,0:07:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要跟著真白一起去迎接他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.34,0:07:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叔叔寄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很貴耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這算什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不是項鍊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給親愛的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝妳15歲生日快樂 謝爾蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也很棒耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.59,0:08:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我適合…這種衣服嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定適合的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是完整一套女孩用品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.46,0:08:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔為什麼要給我這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳考試似乎很拼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.34,0:08:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連同生日禮物一起慶祝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請成為一個優秀的乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝妳15歲生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.98,0:08:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是幾號？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9月7日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.42,0:08:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我生日耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔好厲害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我自己都忘記了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說是怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡跟妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同一天生日？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白女王也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太湊巧了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢，妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.72,0:09:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就定在9月7日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，是我夢中的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼天的青玉？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是這樣嗎？父親
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是難得生日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼非得去迎接\N那種邊境國家的王子不可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.76,0:09:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是聽說那個王子長得很俊秀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:09:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且就是那麼一回事吧\N衛士長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎接一國王子的工作\N還是得靠真白女王…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們…瞞著我什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這種事，是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.78,0:10:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好沒有洩底
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她知道這是相親的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.75,0:10:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛士長，不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，等等嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.04,0:10:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳幹嘛這麼生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這車站
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起第一次見面時的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候妮娜也像現在這樣\N怒氣沖沖的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.49,0:10:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是有嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:10:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩…迷路了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，妳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.96,0:11:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸跟媽媽呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.77,0:11:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳幹嘛從剛剛就笑瞇瞇的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:11:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得很高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:12:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜很體貼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.69,0:12:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是做很普通的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.52,0:12:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，很普通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢呢，下一班車是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的錶…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，妳啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.41,0:12:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.24,0:12:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，我幫妳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，妳去迎接貴賓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很擅長捉迷藏唷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先繞到前面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那個還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.96,0:13:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個很重要，拜託妳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳肚子餓的話\N我可以給妳錢或任何東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.82,0:13:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.47,0:13:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為一名乙HiME\N怎麼能在人前寬衣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錶…父親的錶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.18,0:14:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不可能游泳追到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經結束啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不脫了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦，笨蛋，別亂看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:14:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命，過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停…停車！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白女王！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，那個錶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我願意給你任何謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊，找到之前都沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是烏鴉卻突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它啣走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪裡的烏鴉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳問我哪裡的，我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.48,0:15:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是這座森林裡面的烏鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一個個問清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.43,0:16:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，那個很重要對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面還掛有\N謝爾蓋給妳的禮物鍊子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日這種東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就定在9月7日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.05,0:16:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼天的青玉？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.72,0:16:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，是我夢中的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的生日，只是剛好…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人的女兒在那一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.41,0:16:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是我用第一份薪水\N買的便宜貨喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要送妳好一點的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:16:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要父親的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂，妮依娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.53,0:17:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼有妳在？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.03,0:17:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼妳到現在才出現？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現在我和父親的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.86,0:17:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還帶著那個貴石
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問妳，為什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.77,0:17:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是妳沒有來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.24,0:17:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親就會永遠只看著我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他只把我當女兒看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.94,0:17:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是這樣，我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.88,0:17:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼，誰要相親啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.29,0:17:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睽違已久的微服出巡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得好好看看\N國民為我慶生的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了，命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.42,0:18:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.06,0:18:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…難道妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳對薛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.86,0:18:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，是王少校
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳喜…喜歡他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.33,0:18:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳又怎樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.04,0:18:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:18:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在健行考試途中\N只有妳們兩人時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼啊，沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.99,0:19:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他救了我\N真的只是這樣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.36,0:19:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那支錶果然還是\N一定得找到不可啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆也說過重要的人給的東西\N是真的很重要的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們兩個在這裡做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是該去迎接日邦格的王子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.19,0:19:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝爾蓋…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.19,0:19:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，照平常習慣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛的事情\N要是跟父親說了就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正要過去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為還有時間，所以繞了點路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繞到這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.17,0:20:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罷，正好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.94,0:20:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明找了那麼久…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是在找這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把學校的工作扔一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.26,0:20:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.29,0:20:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.76,0:20:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看妳也很喜歡這條鍊子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那重新來過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.70,0:20:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的長大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.91,0:20:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們相遇到現在\N正好是第6年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道妮娜妳沒發現？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…這也不怪妳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.12,0:20:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後妳在醫院待了一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:21:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的生日9月7日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們第一天相遇的日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.57,0:21:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.78,0:21:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮依娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.32,0:21:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.60,0:21:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還“怎麼辦”呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.97,0:21:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.18,0:22:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子駕到！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.66,0:22:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.19,0:22:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你們出迎了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.03,0:22:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇氣會實現願望 Do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.93,0:22:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.74,0:22:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只等著我的故事 現在開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.76,0:22:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其逃避 不如挺身面對更好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.56,0:22:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是少女的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.67,0:22:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很努力唷\N就算內心突然感到寂寞的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.21,0:22:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要以笑容面對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.18,0:23:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼NO NO NO 你的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.19,0:23:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有快樂的未來 我想守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.39,0:23:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.56,0:23:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄的心意 比寶石更耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.00,0:23:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出自信向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.04,0:23:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.69,0:23:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔～
